   <div id="mainContent">
   <h1><em>What Role Does the Librarian Play in 21st Century Education?</em></h1>
   <p>School Library Media Specialist... Information Professional... Librarian...</p>
<p>Teacher... Collaborator... Counselor... Innovator... </p>
<p>To</em>day's librarian plays many roles in a school; it's no surprise that there are so many ways to describe them. The best school librarians aim to make their school a better environment for learning. By working with teachers to create exctining lessons, helping students conduct succesful research, encouraging technological and media literacy, and raising awareness of censorship and intellectual property issues. </p>
